# Test reward configuration API

### Get current reward config
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reward-config

### Set ENB rewards
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reward-config
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "ENB",
  "amount": "1000.000",
  "description": "1000 ENB weekly tournament"
}

### Set USDC rewards
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reward-config
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "USDC", 
  "amount": "500.00",
  "description": "500 USDC monthly competition"
}

### Set ETH rewards (back to default)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reward-config
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "ETH",
  "amount": "1.000",
  "description": "1.000 ETH reward pool"
}

# Get current config
curl http://localhost:3000/api/reward-config

# Set ENB rewards
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/reward-config \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"symbol": "ENB", "amount": "1000.000", "description": "1000 ENB weekly tournament"}'